sources.title: The Dancing Pirate (1936) FRANK MORGAN
sources.description:
Stars: Frank Morgan,Charles Collins, Steffi Duna 
Director: Lloyd Corrigan

In this comedy adventure, when a Boston dance teacher gets shanghaied by Pirates his next steps might be dancing off the plank! Co-stars Frank Morgan -- The Wizard of Oz!  Also watch for a very young RITA HAYWORTH a.k.a.  Margarita Carmen Cansino as a member of The Dancing Cansinos.
